flect the foundational strategic value that it provides to us in bolstering the growth of our Connectivity and AI segments."** Its true value is measured by how its low-cost, high-cadence, and reusable launch capabilities enable the rapid and cost-effective deployment of the company\'s internal AI and satellite constellations.',
